citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:13AM on 23-
MAR-2022.
Contacted the licensee via phone but there was no answer. A voice message was left. The licensee's wife was then
contacted. She stated that the licensee was out of town and would not be available for an inspection today.
Additional Inspectors:
CARRIE BONGARD, ANIMAL CARE INSPECTOREnd Section
